title: List of Molde FK seasons
text: This is a list of seasons played by <a href="Molde%20FK">Molde Fotballklubb</a> in Norwegian and European <a href="association%20football">football</a>, regional league seasons from 1915 to 1937 and national league seasons from 1937–38 to the most recent completed season. It details the club's achievements in major competitions, and the top scorers for some season. The statistics is up to date as of the end of the <a href="2020%20Molde%20FK%20season">2020 season</a>.
